---
layout: null
permalink: /offline-manifest.json
sitemap: false
---
{%- comment -%}
  全站离线清单。SW 不直接读这个文件，前端 JS 抓下来后挑选 URL 通过
  postMessage('PREFETCH_URLS', { urls, assets }) 喂给 sw.js。

  不要在这里塞 _site/files/ 下的大照片：那批走"按需下载"按钮，默认不强迫所有访客下 150 MB。
  HTML 内的 <img src> 由 SW 解析时自动跟进缓存（extractAssetUrls）。
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign pages = "" | split: "" -%}
{%- for p in site.pages -%}
  {%- assign u = p.url -%}
  {%- unless u contains ".xml" or u contains ".json" or u contains ".txt" or u == "/sw.js" or u == "/CNAME" or u == "" -%}
    {%- assign pages = pages | push: u -%}
  {%- endunless -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- for p in site.posts -%}
  {%- assign pages = pages | push: p.url -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- for p in site.notes -%}
  {%- assign pages = pages | push: p.url -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{
  "version": "{{ site.time | date: '%Y%m%d%H%M%S' }}",
  "generated": "{{ site.time | date_to_xmlschema }}",
  "pages": {{ pages | uniq | jsonify }},
  "assets": [
    "/manifest.json",
    "/search.json",
    "/assets/css/games-shell.css",
    "/assets/js/games-shell/leaderboard.js",
    "/assets/js/games-shell/comments.js",
    "/assets/js/games-shell/identity.js",
    "/assets/js/games-shell/save-state.js",
    "/assets/js/games-shell/settings-panel.js",
    "/assets/js/games-shell/settlement.js",
    "/assets/js/games-shell/wins-leaderboard.js",
    "/assets/js/games-shell/nick-prompt.js",
    "/assets/js/games-shell/pause-controls.js",
    "/assets/lib/chess.min.js"
  ]
}
